{"tid":1473101,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"8964學運領袖王丹：中共派一些人用苦肉計，故意挑釁示威民眾","createTime":"2019-08-14T18:03:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T00:53:10.000Z","uid":307414,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3c6010fc99d81f593ca954dddc8c4643cf4081a0","tid":1473101,"uid":307414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:03:39.000Z","msg":"1989年六四前夕，中共就曾經把一輛破舊的軍車丟棄在長安街上，然後把上車檢查的民眾誣指為「搶奪軍車，準備暴亂」，為六四開槍製造口實。<br />\n<br />\n現在中共故技重施，派一些人用苦肉計，故意挑釁示威民眾，拍下被毆打照片，在中國民眾中製造「香港人毆打中國人」的假新聞，也是為以後可能的鎮壓製造口實。<br />\n<br />\n我一個過來人，一看就知道中共要幹什麼。因此在這裡誠懇呼籲香港示威者：對於故意挑釁的人，不理他們便是，讓他們自我表演，把他們當空氣就好。<br />\n<br />\n同時也要呼籲外界一定要明辨是非：<br />\n<br />\n第一，我們要相信示威者的理性，相信他們不會無緣無故暴力攻擊無辜者。正常人都不可能自己給自己入罪。<br />\n<br />\n第二，我們一定要知道，很多暴力衝突，其實是中共派人假裝成示威者所為。這方面，他們是慣犯。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E7%8E%8B%E4%B8%B9%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99-Wang-Dans-Page-105759983026/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E7%258E%258B%25E4%25B8%25B9%25E7%25BD%2591%25E7%25AB%2599-Wang-Dans-Page-105759983026%2F&d=uCt0JTl3CznPmZ5dgdQeg2yprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=65bc5b20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/%E7%8E%8B%E4%B8%B9%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99-Wang-Dans-Page-105759983026/</a><br />\n<br />\n／／真心覺得佢寫野都有的point<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />巴打們可以睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋向佢作為民主運動既先驅致敬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(btw P牌第一次出post，有錯屌細力的<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"14ad9649f5d5b49b274f222777c9e73133dc0a5d","tid":1473101,"uid":54431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T22:26:29.000Z","msg":"要比更多人睇<br />\n811 721"},{"pid":"a1ffada808e8e422cc4a5cc2df07eef6c0351ca9","tid":1473101,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T23:27:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32e33f80596409c36479a827d82ae2a2f21d74a3","tid":1473101,"uid":73504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:53:10.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}